title: #92Noon! Carter/Snob/Micheletti/Birk
description: Ryan Carter joins out of the gate to look back at las night's Wild loss in Edmonton, Stump the Snob! finishes the first hour, thoughts on high schools postponing football and volleyball until the spring, Matt Birk joins for most of the final hour!
